00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.440
In general when you work with a brand, you receive a brief,

00:01:42.480 --> 00:01:44.400
a sort of book,

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:45.640
and they tell you this is what we want to do.

00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:48.360
Add a little creativity.

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:51.080
The invitation was very different in this regard. It was like,

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:53.440
put the car to test in any way you can think of.

00:01:53.440 --> 00:01:54.520
Test it in the most exotic,

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:56.120
craziest ways possible.

00:01:56.160 --> 00:02:00.160
The idea is to see that the car is ready to take on anything a person can think of.

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:02.600
Having such a broad scope

00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:04.240
made for a very interesting process,

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:06.280
and we had ideas that were really crazy,

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:09.600
and those are the ones that we are using.

